level.text: This chapter shall apply to applicants for and holders of a license to practice marriage and family therapy.
Chapters 40 (Health Occupations: General Rules) and 41 (Health Occupations: Administrative Procedures) of this title shall supplement this chapter.

level.heading: SOURCE
level.text: As amended by Final Rulemaking published at 53 DCR 7845 (September 29, 2006).
